---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for Name Numerology Hub — learn how we collect, use, and protect your data.">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-zinc-500 mb-10">Last updated: June 20, 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-zinc max-w-none space-y-8 text-zinc-300">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>Welcome to <strong>Name Numerology Hub</strong> ("we," "us," or "our"), operated at <strong>namenumerologyhub.com</strong>. We are committed to protecting your personal information and your right to privacy. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and share information when you visit our website.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect information you voluntarily provide when using our tools (such as names entered into our calculators) and information automatically collected when you visit our site:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Pages visited, time spent, browser type, device type, and IP address (collected by Google Analytics).</li>
          <li><strong>Calculator Inputs:</strong> Names and dates entered into our tools are processed entirely client-side (in your browser) and are never stored on our servers.</li>
          <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> We use cookies for analytics through Google Analytics. You can control cookie settings in your browser.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>To operate, improve, and personalize the website experience.</li>
          <li>To analyze traffic and usage patterns via Google Analytics.</li>
          <li>To comply with legal obligations.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We use the following third-party services that may collect data independently:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> For website traffic analysis. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-cyan-400 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">5. Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use cookies to enhance your experience. You can choose to disable cookies through your browser settings. Note that disabling cookies may affect the functionality of our site.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">6. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We do not store personal data on our servers. All calculator inputs are processed locally in your browser and discarded when you leave the page. Analytics data is retained by Google Analytics per their data retention policies.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Our website is not directed to children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe we have collected information from a child, please contact us immediately.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">8. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Depending on your location, you may have rights under GDPR, CCPA, or other privacy laws, including the right to access, correct, or delete your data. Since we do not store personal calculator inputs, most requests relate to analytics data managed by Google. Contact us at the address below for any privacy requests.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The updated version will be indicated by the "Last updated" date at the top of this page. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">10. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:</p>
        <ul class="list-none space-y-1">
          <li>🌐 Website: <a href="https://namenumerologyhub.com" class="text-cyan-400 hover:underline">namenumerologyhub.com</a></li>
          <li>📧 Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@namenumerologyhub.com" class="text-cyan-400 hover:underline">privacy@namenumerologyhub.com</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
